				<description>&lt;p&gt;All speakers are invited to the speakers dinner at Ostra!&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Agenda:&#xA;18:00 - Drinks and mingling&#xA;18:45 - Dinner&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Do you have any allergies, intolerances or dietary restrictions? Submit them in Sessionize before 5th of March.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;There will be two taxis leaving from the hotel at 17:45 and 18:00.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.openstreetmap.org/directions?engine=fossgis_osrm_foot&amp;amp;route=60.397852%2C5.322499%3B60.378644%2C5.333122#map=14/60.38791/5.33395&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://www.boosterconf.no/2026/images/ostra_walking_map.png&#34; alt=&#34;Walking directions to Ostra&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
